ont><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=244.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> What discipline to specialize in...</span><hr size=1> The EQ guide to Kunark mentions that enchanters have two choices for spell specialization, Alteration which accounts for 80% of our spells, and Conjuration which accounts for the mez spells...<br>
The book recommended specializing in Alteration.  However someone on the message boards recommended Conjuration because the mez is so class defining...<br>
What specialization did you chose, and do you regret your choice now? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :\ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":\"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Thanks,<br>
RosiePosie<br>
19th Enchanter<br>
Luclin Server<br>
Sovereign Storm <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm.showUserPublicProfile?gid=camehleon>CamehLeon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 54<br> <font color=#330000>(2/13/03 5:14:08 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=244.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.ifrance.com/camehlheon/images/camehbourre.gif width=129 height=91></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What discipline to specialize in...</span><hr size=1> I chose Alteration<br>
<br>
I can't say if I regret cause I've never played an enchanter with Conjuration <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
But i'm sure not disappointed <p>
<BR>
<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=10374><img src="http://www.morosa.f9.co.uk/cameh.jpg"></a> <BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#deddbf><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub136.ezboard.com/beqenchantersrealm.showUserPublicProfile?gid=charmroxors>Charmroxors</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#330000>(2/17/03 1:33:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=244.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What discipline to specialize in...</span><hr size=1> i chose alteration... my buddy (60chanter) went with conjuration...i've never seen a difference between our mezzing abilities, as long as your conjuration skill is fine (you mez often) then you'll be alright <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
